				ul.service-list
					li ART DIRECTING
					li FILM MAKING
					li PHOTOGRAPHY
					li EDITING
			.col-right 
				.content-box.max-w-xl
					p.body-1.mb-6 We're a artistic duo based in Saigon one directs, the other makes sure it doesn't look ugly.
					p.body-1.mb-6 Somewhere between an art director and a photographer, we argue about light, eat too much street food, and somehow still make films together.
					p.body-1.mb-10 Let's make something cool together. Or just say hi: hello@changwangpictures.com
					a(href="./contact.html").link-arrow.inline-flex.items-center.gap-2.uppercase.font-bold CONTACT 
						i.fa-regular.fa-arrow-right

